  "texts": [
    "BS: HHMI Chief of Strategic Initiatives.",
    "DT: Science Program Officer at the Chan Zuckerberg Initiative.",
    "The CZI Open Science program supports bioRxiv, medRxiv, ASAPbio, as well as several projects related to preprint curation and open peer review.",
    "RV: I am a co-founder of ASAPbio, which promotes the use of preprints in the life sciences and preprint review initiatives.",
    "I am co-founder of Review Commons, a journalindependent peer review platform."
  ]
}